    <ul>
        <li>Traefik or Nginx Proxy Manager</li>
        <li>Portainer</li>
        <li>Grafana + Prometheus</li>
        <li>Uptime Kuma</li>
        <li>Internal dashboards</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Goals</h2>
    <p>
        Build reliable, self-hosted alternatives to cloud SaaS and document deployment strategies.
